00:02:51.500 --> 00:02:56.620
It had fighting, leveling-up, and the ability to create guilds, or like-minded groups within the game.

00:02:56.620 --> 00:03:00.900
This would become a cornerstone of modern MMORPGs and the communities created within them.

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:06.120
